# Patents

Title: Prioritizer system for target acquisition
Number: 8,275,205
Issued: September 25, 2012
Co-inventors: Saad Bedros, Ben Miller

System for prioritizing the target acquisition of faces for a system requiring
high-resolution facial images from a distance for tasking of a pan-tilt camera
system.  Generalized to algorithm for choosing targets based on current location
and candidate locations for minimizing required effort and maximizing target
capture.

